scgcf_clarity
=============

Custom scripting for GenoLogics (http://www.genologics.com) Clarity LIMS for the Single Cell Genomics Core Facility (SCGCF) at Wellcome Trust Sanger Institute.

Forked from wtsi_clarity on 21st May 2015

TESTING

$ cd src/perl
$ perl Build.PL
$ ./Build test

or

$ TEST_AUTHOR=1  ./Build test

to run an individual test:
$ ./Build test --verbose --test-files t/mytest.t

to run groups of tests:
$ ./Build test --verbose --test-files 't/00-*.t' # note the quotes


